## File Formatting

Files end with newline, no trailing whitespace. See `~/.claude/formatter-reference.md`

- **Prettier**: Installed locally — use `prettier` directly (not `npx`)

## Commit Messages

Use conventional commits (`feat:`, `fix:`, `refactor:`, etc.)

### Co-Authored-By & Flair

**⚠️ BEFORE every commit/PR/MR**, run `git remote -v` to determine the remote — then use the matching format. **Never guess, never ask.**

#### Commits

| Remote | Co-Authored-By |
|--------|---------------|
{{- if .isWork }}
| KN GitLab (`gitlab.example.com`) | `Co-Authored-By: <Character> <email>` |
{{- end }}
| Everything else (GitHub, other GitLab, etc.) | `Co-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>` |

**No quotes in commits** — quotes are exclusively for MR/PR descriptions.

#### MR/PR descriptions (not commits!)

| Remote | Footer |
|--------|--------|
