{{- end }}
| Everything else (GitHub, other GitLab, etc.) | `🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)` |
{{- if .isWork }}

**KN GitLab flair**: Match character/quote vibe to the change (bug fix → John Wick, delete → Thanos). Vary each commit. See `~/.claude/commit-flair.md`
